.SH NAME
.PP
conn \- Set Sdb connection for the DiagLog object
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]diaglog.search().conn(<Sdb>)\f[]
.PP
\f[B]diaglog.collect().conn(<Sdb>)\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
DiagLog
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Set Sdb connection for the DiagLog object, which is used by the DiagLog object
to get cluster information.
If only search local files.
this function does not need to be used.
