> var diaglog = new DiagLog()
\f[]
.fi
.RE
.IP \[bu] 2
Search for the most recent log with error \-79, including the log following the
error, and limit the returned results to 10
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> diaglog.search().error( \-79 ).limit( 10 ).after( 1 ).conn(db)
/tmp/sequoiadb/search/cluster_2025\-01\-01\-12:01:01.000.auto 
\f[]
.fi
.RE
